        <body>
      
		<pb n="1"/>
			<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Pittsburgh</placeName> <date>November the 10<hi rend="sup">th</hi> 5613</date></p>
          <p rend="indent(2)">Revd Sir</p>
          <p rend="indent(1)">The Occident this morning is come to hand I took notice<lb/> there&#44; that your translation on the bible is all ready till<lb/> the first of <persName>Samuel</persName>&#44; I hope you will <sic>recolect</sic> that <persName>Mr Celner</persName><lb/> of <placeName>Montgomery</placeName>&#44; wrote once to you in my name&#44; that I wish<lb/> to take one of them. I therefore beg of you&#44; to be so kind as<lb/> to inform me about it every thing particularly I am very desirous<lb/> for it&#44; if it is any thing to be done for you here&#44; you have only to<lb/> command. I am with the greatest pleasure to your service<lb/> at any time. I hope I will soon be able to write in the<lb/> Occident&#44; with the help of our God&#44; I speak a great deal better<lb/> than I do write&#44; but I hope in a short time to be able in writing<lb/> to&#44; the five dollars I will send you please god with <persName>Mr<lb/> Jaruslawsky</persName> as I have written.&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;I am</p>
          <p rend="indent(10)">Sir</p>
          <p rend="indent(8)">Your most <sic>respecfuly</sic> humble servt</p>
          <p rend="indent(9)"><persName role="author">E. Marcuson</persName></p>
			<p>have you any news&#63;</p>
			<p>I wrote this in great hurry. I have to go to the hospital&#44; an Israelite is<lb/> there.</p>
		<pb n="2"/>
			<p><addressee>Revd Isaac Leeser</addressee></p>
          <p rend="indent(1)"><placeName>371 Walnut Street</placeName></p>
          <p rend="indent(2)"><placeName>Philadelphia</placeName></p>
          <p rend="indent(3)"><placeName>Pa</placeName></p>
			<p>Paid</p>
          
        </body>
